version_description:
Thank you for choosing Device Monitor²! We always do our best to make the app faster, more stable and easier to use.
Update to the latest version to discover all the new features.
• fixed the bug caused to appear the function to empty the RAM inside the PRO Kit.

In addition with the recent version 3.0.0 you will also have:This version contains the following changes:
• added the new "Test Kit" to test most of the sensors of the device;
• added support for Apple Pencil, flashlight, motion coprocessor and screen mirroring;
• speeded up the RAM cleaning system (now part of the "PRO Kit");
• fix for fetch of public IP address;
• other minor fix.

NOTE: whoever purchased the "PRO Kit" has the right to have the "Test Kit" free of charge. To do this, simply reset the in-app purchases from the settings page within the app.

Do you like our app? Tell us your opinion, it can help us improve the application! Remember that we listen to the feedback from each of you!

